r item number. It is not allowed to mix different part numbers in a handling unit. Different modification /different revision levels of products also may not be combined in a handling unit. Packages must be easily handled during opening and closing and for repacking operations. All handling units must enable stacking, be rigid with no excessive flexing, bowing, buckling or distortion. They must provide adequate protection to ensure that goods reach end user in perfect condition. Depending on the shipping conditions and components material e.g. for sea-freight conditions, environmental effects could require additional packaging material as desiccant bags, VCI (Volatile Corrosion Inhibitor)"
