ppliers must use packaging that withstands the various dynamics of all transportation methods as land, air and sea transport. Only one-part number is permitted to be shipped inside each box. Multiple part numbers inside one box is not permitted. 4.2.2 Packaging Design & Dimensions In order to enable a maximum fill rate of the pallet and the pallet footprint the container shall be modular. The preferred container dimension for the 1.200mm x 800mm footprint can be found in the following attachment: EA-SC (Significant/Special Characteristic)-xx-M-001-A-01. The corrugated material must have minimum 44 ECT (Edge Crush Test) to provide a sufficient strength"
}


